        "evidence": "<p dir=\"ltr\">The following three criteria must be fulfilled for the last 3 months with symptom onset &ge;6 months ago:</p>\n<ol>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Must have &ge;2 of the following, each for &gt;1/4 (25%) of defecations except (f):</p>\n</li>\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-latin;\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Straining.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Lumpy or hard stools (form 1 or 2 on the Bristol Stool Form Scale - see below).</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Sensation of incomplete evacuation.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Sensation of anorectal obstruction/blockage.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Manual maneuvers to facilitate defecation (e.g. digital evacuation, pelvic floor support).</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&lt;3 spontaneous bowel movements per week.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Loose stools rarely present without use of laxatives.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Does not meet <calculator id=\"4007\">Rome IV Criteria for IBS.</calculator></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Bristol Stool Form Scale:</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><img src=\"https://cdn-web-img.mdcalc.com/content/romeiv-bristol.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\" /></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-f138cc41-f8ec-fbf9-f023-47b76d500ad4\">From <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4760857/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Chumpitazi 2016</a>.</p>",
